Successfully migrated from an aging Motorola MG8702 modem/router combo to a modern networking solution using the Hitron CODA56 DOCSIS 3.1 Cable Modem and TP-Link Archer BE550 Pro BE9700 Wi-Fi 7 Router. Improved network reliability, increased future scalability, maintained wired office connectivity, and successfully integrated existing smart home devices with the new network infrastructure.